Matches featured:  • Charlie Haas vs. Paul London  • Batista, Cryme Tyme (JTG & Shad) & John Cena vs. Cody Rhodes, John Bradshaw Layfield, Kane & Ted DiBiase  • Jimmy Wang Yang vs. The Great Khali (w/Ranjin Singh)  • Jeff Hardy vs. Edge.  Date:	28.07.2008  Promotion:	World Wrestling Entertainment  Type:	TV-Show  Location:	Washington, District Of Columbia, USA  Arena:	Verizon Center  Broadcast type:	Taped  Broadcast date:	02.08.2008  TV station/network:	NBC  TV rating:	1.4  Commentary by:	Jim Ross, Jerry Lawler & CM Punk.
